{"text_id":37753,"tokens":["The"," potential"," benefits"," of"," technology"," that"," can"," detect"," human"," emotions"," and"," moods"," are"," numerous"," and"," far","-","reaching","."," From"," classroom"," settings",","," to"," advertising"," and"," even"," mental"," health"," therapy",","," technology"," that"," can"," detect"," and"," respond"," to"," our"," emotions"," has"," the"," power"," to"," revolution","ize"," and"," greatly"," enhance"," many"," aspects"," of"," our"," daily"," lives",".","\n","In"," a"," classroom"," setting",","," a"," teacher"," or"," educator"," would"," have"," the"," ability"," to"," instantly"," assess"," how"," a"," student"," is"," feeling","."," By"," recognizing"," subtle"," changes"," in"," body"," language"," and"," facial"," expressions",","," a"," teacher"," could"," quickly"," gain"," insight"," into"," a"," student","'","s"," mood"," and"," react"," accordingly","."," Additionally",","," technology"," could"," be"," used"," to"," assist"," students"," with"," special"," needs"," or"," learning"," disabilities","."," For"," example",","," it"," could"," be"," used"," to"," detect"," heightened"," levels"," of"," anxiety"," in"," a"," student"," with"," autism",","," allowing"," the"," teacher"," to"," respond"," and"," provide"," the"," necessary"," support",".","\n","Ad","vertisers"," could"," also"," benefit"," from"," technology"," that"," can"," detect"," emotions","."," By"," monitoring"," customers","\u2019"," expressions"," and"," reactions"," in"," real","-","time",","," advertisers"," could"," better"," tailor"," their"," products"," and"," promotions"," to"," the"," emotions"," of"," their"," target"," audience","."," For"," example",","," a"," car"," company"," could"," quickly"," learn"," if"," a"," customer"," is"," feeling"," excited"," or"," frustrated",","," and"," adjust"," the"," pitch"," of"," their"," salesperson"," accordingly","."," ","\n","Finally",","," technology"," that"," can"," detect"," emotion"," could"," be"," greatly"," beneficial"," to"," mental"," health"," therapy","."," A"," therapist"," could"," use"," this"," technology"," to"," identify"," shifts"," in"," their"," patient","'","s"," emotions"," during"," a"," session","."," This"," would"," not"," only"," help"," the"," therapist"," better"," understand"," their"," patient",","," but"," it"," would"," also"," enable"," them"," to"," provide"," more"," targeted"," and"," individualized"," treatment",".","\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," potential"," benefits"," of"," technology"," that"," can"," detect"," human"," emotions"," and"," moods"," are"," vast"," and"," wide","-","reaching","."," From"," classrooms"," to"," advertising"," and"," even"," mental"," health"," therapy",","," this"," technology"," has"," the"," potential"," to"," revolution","ize"," our"," daily"," lives"," in"," exciting"," and"," meaningful"," ways","."," It"," can"," also"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," into"," our"," emotional"," states",","," enabling"," us"," to"," better"," understand"," and"," respond"," to"," our"," own"," emotions"," in"," positive"," ways","."," Therefore",","," it"," is"," clear"," to"," see"," that"," this"," technology"," could"," be"," hugely"," beneficial"," in"," many"," different"," settings","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"text-davinci-003","label":1}